      "task_description": "Implemented Parikshak, a fully deterministic engineering task evaluation system using FastAPI (Python 3.11), React 18, TailwindCSS, and Pydantic v2. The system enforces a strict 8-step locked pipeline across layered api/, service/, model/, and core/ directory structure.\r\n\r\nPipeline flow: REVIEW_PACKET hard gate, registry validation, signal collection via SignalEngine, domain routing for backend and frontend detection, binary rule engine evaluation with 4 checks, decision engine, human-in-loop escalation, mandatory JSONL bucket logging, Niyantran deterministic task graph selection.\r\n\r\nRule engine performs 4 binary checks in strict order: schema validation, completeness validation, logic validation, integration validation. Output contract is exact: evaluation_result PASS or FAIL, failure_type, selected_task_id, selection_reason, source task_graph. System passes 6/6 BHIV determinism test cases with identical outputs across repeated runs.",
